<subSubSection id="54C9202DC56E2DC7AA1C40F8E3A50681" pageId="null" pageNumber="518" type="description">
<paragraph id="BF76834947C6889484F9DC07831D978E" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="FB00C9704E4A4082CB079B92C63E5615" class="Liliopsida" family="Juncaceae" genus="Luzula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="518" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nemorosa">
<emphasis id="AB77B9A0B2C9AF725FC1497524845A4D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<authorityName id="8CB52F1D43C8CBA541AB6DEA7FECA268" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">L.</authorityName>
nemorosa
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="35B2DDECF25B1F1F73651E095566CBC4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<normalizedToken id="E1B30640509A745493085D89948D0A81" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
rein 
<normalizedToken id="8A109D1BA4542A5E2B265E52A3FF02D3" originalValue="weiβ" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">weiβ</normalizedToken>
,die innern ca. 5 mm lang; reife Frucht etwa
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="86691AD7CF0D772327E9F693A8EA7F93" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="FC86D275B1797A2BE2263C75A1B721E9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="A43E6ED77DF1E70AE163548F44D40E29" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Samen ca. 1,5 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="C70FF53BA2953A98CD2426B4DE114A23" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EE6276A89123E2680504DADA9615F98A" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis id="668B6C28AFA87A2EFE62B60CA8DBE537" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 12:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Tessin (Tesserete) und aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="980993F02AA14707D5B62DC01134C266" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="3B9A07D9362764D578C6CE0018C77F29" originalValue="Nordenskiöld" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Nordenskioeld</normalizedToken>
1951).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="991F2FD2893AAE236E59DD340D1071C8" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis id="546A251B8353433C87287E871348A8B5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin, seltener kollin. Humose 
<normalizedToken id="C670158979C7B974B310722FB648C14A" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Laub- und 
<normalizedToken id="847938151FA367C6CCE0791752C89B8C" originalValue="Nadelwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Nadelwaelder</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8245EE6CD807FA416E3ECFAFF783F98E" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis id="2F49C15E084071FBC47829DFA837994B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="0A6F004C2C01FB70EE3E1863337E9FF9" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="6B07EDF4839A9182A19FC618F4E93E3B" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Cevennen, Gebiet der obern Loire, 
<normalizedToken id="A8CD8F45B101379EB8C889EDEDF94CB4" originalValue="Südjura" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Suedjura</normalizedToken>
, Alpen (
<normalizedToken id="602F63177E0AB195CB4CE08899C540D4" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Brandenberg in den Nordtiroler Kalkalpen, Brenner und Lienz), Karpaten (?), Apennin (
<normalizedToken id="4B4483E85329043E2911FED9C07141F3" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Tuskien). Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1964). - Im Gebiet: Alpen (Zentral- und 
<normalizedToken id="0B17F7079B90B6006312551F58CF5703" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="482B36C97095BAB50D98082837B59D7A" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">haeufig</normalizedToken>
), Voralpen, Jura (von Westen her bis in den Neuenburger Jura), Molasseberge im Mittelland (selten, z.B. Irchel).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
